experts believe : insurance QDII will not divert domestic stock market funds in the short term
chinanews , july 30
according to a report by the china securities daily , a few days ago , the " interim procedures for the management of overseas investment of insurance funds " were promulgated , and insurance funds have a broader scope for the use of the capital market .
Liu lefei , chief investment officer of china life stock company , believes that with the appreciation of the renminbi and the improvement of the domestic capital market , insurance institutions will not make large - scale overseas investments through foreign exchange purchases in the short term , which also means that insurance QDII will not divert domestic stock market funds in the short term .
according to the report , many insurance organizations hold the same view .
experts say that since there is currently no renminbi derivatives market and insurance institutions do not have sufficient means to avoid risks , the time is not ripe for large - scale foreign exchange purchases .
Liu lefei said : in the long run , in terms of asset allocation , overseas investment should occupy a certain proportion of the overall allocation of insurance companies .
however , in view of the relatively strong upward pressure on the renminbi at present , china life will mainly use its own foreign exchange funds to make overseas investments .
foreign exchange purchases for overseas investment should be handled with caution under the present circumstances .
( SHANG Xiaoyang )
China directly loses 52.5 billion yuan in flood prevention this year
the reporter learned from the state flood control and drought relief headquarters : as of 29 july , 118 million mu of flooded crops across the country had been affected , of which 54.14 million mu had been damaged , 119.15 million people had been affected , 652 people had died as a result of the disaster , 452,000 houses had collapsed , and direct economic losses amounted to 52.5 billion yuan .
across the country , 140 million mu of farmland has been affected by drought , and 5.88 million people and 4.7 million large livestock have had temporary difficulties in drinking water because of the drought .
on 29 july , the state general headquarters for flood prevention and drought relief made an emergency deployment in view of the current grim situation of flood prevention and drought relief .
he called on all provinces along the Huai he and the flood control headquarters of the Huai he to step up control , strengthen the defense of embankments during the receding period , and win an all - round victory in flood control and flood control along the Huai he .
the state general administration of flood prevention , together with the financial , agricultural , and other departments , has sent three working groups to the frontline of flood prevention and the drought - stricken areas to guide flood prevention and drought relief work .
at present , flood control and flood control work on the Huaihe river is proceeding in an intense and orderly manner , flood control works are running normally , the Huaihong new river of the Huaihe river is also being flooded , and 268,000 people in Henan , Anhui , and Jiangsu provinces are sticking to the embankments of the Huaihe river .
there is no great danger in the embankment of the main stream of the Huai river .
Heilongjiang , Jiangxi , and other provinces launched an emergency drought - relief response in accordance with the plan , and drought - relief work is being carried out in an intense and orderly manner .
