Chen shui - Bian secretly criticized the judicial intervention in the election , which was denied by the Taiwan judicial yuan and asked for an explanation .
chinanews , july 31 - Chen shui - Bian questioned on the 30th the attempt of judicial personnel on the island to intervene in the election of the leader of the Taiwan region .
on the same day , Tseng Kao - Kim - chih , director of the administration department of Taiwan 's senate court , said that the current performance of the judges on the island did not conform to what Chen shui - Bian said , and asked Chen shui - Bian to explain his remarks .
according to a report by Taiwan 's lien - ho PAO , Chen shui - Bian questioned judges , prosecutors , or investigators on 30 june . due to political factors or election considerations , he intervened in , influenced , and even attempted to influence the campaign activities of candidates of various political parties . he said he hoped that this phenomenon would not exist in Taiwan , but it might be very difficult .
in response to Chen shui - Bian 's question , Taiwan justice president tan Weng - Yue - Sheng did not respond with a low - key tone , while Tseng fan Kwong - Chun appointed Gao jinzhi to speak on behalf of Tseng jia court .
Gao jinzhi said : both the Taiwan fundamental law and judge Heng 's code explicitly state that judges should not participate in party activities or assist in elections , that judges are very careful to abide by the relevant restrictions , and that he believes that judges have done a good job .
Gao jinzhi pointed out , for example , that judge Chang Sheng - Hee of Kaohsiung high school took part in the Kedaglan school course a few years ago , that is , a self-discipline committee composed of judges decided to punish him for the political nature of the course .
Chang Sheng - Hee once wanted to participate in the primary election of the democratic progressive party , but because of a dispute over running for office , he finally decided to give up .
Gao jinzhi held that if there is relief at the trial level in individual cases , it is not possible to infer that the judge has another political intention simply on the basis of winning or losing the verdict .
Germany to lower entry threshold for professionals
Xinhua news agency , Berlin , july 1 , by wire ( reporter huaicheng wang )
German minister of education and scientific research savan said a few days ago that Germany should lower the restrictions on the introduction of foreign professionals in the " immigration law " and resolve the shortage of professional personnel in Germany by increasing the introduction of foreign personnel .
according to the oecd report , Germany 's labor force between the ages of 15 and 64 will decline year by year by 2010 .
if there are not enough immigrants , Germany 's labor force will be reduced by 6 percent by 2020 .
however , reports from the german employers ' federation , the german engineers ' association , and other organizations show that there is a big shortage of engineers and professional and technical personnel in the german labor market at present .
according to the data of the german federal labor office , in may this year , the supply gap of engineers in the german labor market was about 12.7 - million , and the supply gap of technicians was about 9,600 .
in order to protect the employment of its own people , Germany has set a relatively high threshold for the introduction of foreign talents .
Germany 's " immigration law " stipulates that professionals from non - eu countries must earn no less than 85,500 euros a year in Germany , otherwise they cannot obtain work and residence permits in Germany .
Savan suggested that the limit be lowered to 40,000 to 60,000 euros .
don &apos;t believe in the theory of law
article 8 of the draft amendment to the " lawyers law , " which was recently submitted to the NPC standing committee for deliberation , stipulates that persons who have engaged in legal research , teaching , and other professional work , and who possess a high professional title or equivalent professional level , may be allowed to practice law upon examination and approval by the judicial administration department of the state council .
( China youth daily , june 28 )
in legal terms , there is the division between the theoretical circle and the practical circle . the former mainly includes such abstract behaviors as legal teaching and research work , while the latter is more engaged in litigation , legal consultation , and legal services .
for a long time , there has been a phenomenon of people in the legal theory and the real world being in a light of each other 's likes . the real world is thought to lack the necessary legal literacy in the real world and to be a mechanical legalist in the real world , while the real world 's criticism of the real world is pointed to the fact that the real world is unable to guide the practice of the theory .
with regard to such differences in division of labor , what the law can do is to remain neutral , and not to strongly support either side .
however , the paralegal system in the " lawyer law " objectively recognizes that the legal theory field is superior to the legal practice field .
in fact , some experts and scholars engaged in the study and teaching of legal history , international law and other pure legal theories , no matter how advanced their theoretical attainments , are incompatible with the practice of law .
in this way , there is no doubt that the establishment of a special lawyer system has opened up an extremely unfavorable and bad situation for the confusion of the qualifications of the legal and practical circles .
these are not the only superstitions about the tan theorists , such as the phenomenon that expert opinions and expert panel discussions often influence or even negate court decisions , and this is also a direct manifestation of this superstition .
