it is indeed worth advocating if this example is to motivate other LSS officers to extricate themselves from difficulties through their own efforts , and it would be naive to use it to enlist the support of those who have cheated the LSS for a long time .
in the work of distinguishing between genuine and fake low - security households , more reliance should be placed on the law .
relevant departments should strengthen the obligations that must be fulfilled by low - income households when enjoying low - income insurance : for example , they should promptly report changes in family members and income , report employment , and undergo periodic review , while relevant departments should step up supervision and inspection .
