Hong kong celebrates 10 years of reunification
on 1 july , the alarm bell of the jinghai temple memorial hall in Nanjing was struck again and the bell sounded melodiously .
this heavy historical echo was shared by the citizens of the mainland and Hong kong , Nanjing , and Hong kong compatriots , Heng tianya , through the television station 's televised link to mark the 10 th anniversary of Hong kong 's return to the motherland .
ten years ago , at midnight on 1 july , 155 alarm bells rang over the bell tower of the Jinghai temple memorial hall in Nanjing to bid farewell to the humiliating history of the cession of Hong kong island .
in front of the small memorial hall , people from all walks of life in Nanjing gathered together . they said that they would ring the alarm bell through their own hands and always warn themselves and future generations not to forget history .
the bell was 1.842 meters high , and 1842 coincided with the signing of the " Nanjing treaty " during the outbreak of the opium war .
the shoulder height is 1.997 metres and 1997 is the year of Hong kong 's reunification .
Wang fengling , the planner and miner of the world alarm bell , explained that the five tongwang characters revolve around the body of the bell , the bronze bell uses high relief , two dragons hold up fireballs , symbolizing that Hong kong is the eastern pearl of the motherland , and finally , Nanjing city 's plum blossom is used as the impact pattern of the bell body .
Yu xiaodong , the first democratic party figure to propose the construction of an alarm clock in those years , said in general terms that it had been 10 years since Hong kong 's return to the motherland . he hoped that Hong kong 's tomorrow would be as bright and melodious as that bell and never cease to stand .
( end ) ( Zhu Xiaoying and Liu Yang )
