Jiangxi province recently decided to award an honorary prize of 30 years ' work in rural sanitation to health professionals who have taken root in rural areas for more than 30 years .
according to a briefing given by the Jiangxi provincial health department , health professionals and technicians who have engaged in health professional and technical work in township and town health centers run by the government , who have a medical education or higher and a technical title of health professional or higher at the primary level , and who have worked in township and town health centers , township blood prevention teams , and leprosy villages for more than 30 years on the job , will all be awarded prizes .
