Qingdao , july 26 ( reporter song xuechun , correspondent fan zhongliang )
from 20 july to 10 august ( every Monday , Wednesday , and august ) , the Shandong Jiaozhou city traffic police brigade carried out activities in the city people 's square , jialejia square , sanlihe square , shinan district , ligezhuang square , jiaobei town , Kowloon town , jiaodong town , and fuan industrial park to send traffic safety films to communities ( villages ) and work sites .
before the opening of the film , the traffic police brigade distributed to the public the publication " staying away from traffic accidents and protecting lives -- a letter to the broad masses of citizens " and some propaganda materials , and broadcast the special traffic films " warning of traffic accidents on life " and " on the way to school . "
the tragic scenes in the film caused people to marvel one after another , and bloody scenes played an extremely warning role .
in particular , the special feature film " on the way to school " , in the form of cartoons , made primary school students easy to understand and love to watch , and received a profound education .
the film attracted more than 3,000 residents from around the square , especially some young people and migrant workers who came to jiaozhou to work . they all sat in the middle of the square and watched it with relish .
by sending traffic safety films to communities ( villages ) and construction sites , the broad masses of citizens , while enjoying the cool air , also received profound traffic safety education , and were warmly welcomed by the citizens , especially the new citizens .
Ministry of health : nationwide catering industry to gradually implement hygiene supervision and publicity system
in order to better implement the " food hygiene law " and the state council 's " decision on further strengthening food safety work , " the ministry of health has carried out experiments in 10 localities , including Haidian district of beijing municipality , Tianjin municipality , Taizhou city and jiangyan city of Jiangsu province , Hangzhou city of Zhejiang province , Luoyang city of Henan province , Wuhan city of Hubei province , Haikou city , Sanya city of Hainan province , and Chengdu city of Sichuan province , to publicize the hygiene supervision of catering units .
this system will also be gradually extended to the whole country .
on the basis of routine hygiene supervision , the food and beverage industry hygiene supervision and publicity system carries out on - the - spot supervision and inspection of nine important hygiene conditions in food and beverage units , such as hygiene permits , hygiene management system , health management personnel , labels of food quality and labels , hygiene protection during the food processing process , environmental hygiene in processing plants , cleaning and disinfection of food and beverage utensils , and purchase of major raw materials . based on the inspection results , the assessment conclusion is drawn that the hygienic condition of the beverage is good , the hygienic condition of the beverage is generally good , and the hygienic condition of the beverage is relatively poor .
according to reports , the public form will follow the uniform colors and styles prescribed by the ministry of health . it will include the results of on - the - spot inspections of nine hygiene conditions , comprehensive evaluation conclusions , on - the - spot hygiene supervision opinions and the names of the agencies responsible for supervision , as well as customer complaint reporting telephone numbers . it will also be displayed in the foyer of the inspected catering unit or in the conspicuous location of the customer entrance so as to facilitate customers ' understanding of the hygiene conditions of the restaurant .
( reporter Hu Qifeng )
security council decides to extend un peacekeeping force in ethiopia
the united nations security council today unanimously approved a six - month extension of the mandate of the united nations peacekeeping force in ethiopia and Eritrea ( UNMEE ) until january 31 .
the resolution demanded that all parties concerned fulfil their commitments , exercise restraint , ease tensions , and refrain from provocative military activities , called on Eritrea to immediately withdraw its troops and heavy military equipment from the Temporary Security Zone , and called on Ethiopia to reduce the number of additional military troops recently deployed in areas adjacent to the Temporary Security Zone .
it demanded that Ethiopia take immediate and concrete steps to enable the EEBC to demarcate the border expeditiously without preconditions ; and demanded that Eritrea lift without further delay or preconditions all restrictions on the movement and operations of UNMEE .
the resolution reiterated its full support for the work of the EEBC and welcomed its decision to hold a meeting with the two sides in new york on september 6 .
in 1998 , border clashes broke out between Eritrea and ethiopia , killing more than 70,000 people .
in june 2000 , the two sides signed a cease - fire agreement in Algiers , the capital of Algeria .
the united nations began deploying peacekeeping troops along the border between ethiopia and Eritrea in july 2001 to supervise the implementation of the ceasefire agreement between the two countries .
( by reporter wu Zhiqiang and wang xiangjiang )
opening ceremony of olympic national county basketball invitational competition
Xinhua news agency , Chengdu , june 30 ,
Xing coral and reporter tian yuan reported : in order to implement the spirit of the instructions of the CPC central committee on building a harmonious socialist society , to coordinate with the building of a new socialist countryside , to sing the theme of national fitness and the olympics , to enrich the cultural and sports life of the masses , and to welcome the olympics , the national county - level basketball invitational competition kicked off in shuangliu county , Chengdu , on 30 april .
the six - day event attracted 10 county - level men 's basketball teams from all over the country .
according to regulations , athletes participating in this competition must be amateurs and must be over 18 years old .
all professional and professional athletes registered at the Basketball Athletes Management Center of the State Sports Administration in 2006 / 07 are not allowed to enter the competition .
the competition adopts the newly approved " basketball rules " of the china basketball association . the competition is divided into two stages : preliminary and final .
the competition was sponsored by the basketball management center of the state general administration of sports , the china basketball association , and the china international sports tourism company .
in recent years , the cultural and sports undertakings in shuangliu county , which has a history of more than 2,000 years , have developed rapidly . shuangliu county has successively won a series of special awards , such as the national sports advanced county in guang and the national mass sports advanced unit in guang .
especially in the construction of new rural areas , shuangliu county has vigorously implemented the peasants ' physical fitness project , combining the construction of sports facilities with the beautification , greening , and brightening of rural areas , building sports stadiums in the rural areas and next to the peasants , allowing the sports service system to cover the rural areas , actively popularizing and developing physical fitness and competition activities with strong local characteristics , which are popular among the peasants , and which are easy to participate in , and improving and improving the peasants ' physical quality .
three main functions of modern military uniforms
the first is the recognition function .
an important symbol that distinguishes between the armed forces of different countries , different arms and services , and between the armed forces and the people .
although the military uniforms of more than 100 countries , large and small , have basically the same purpose , the uniforms of the armed forces of no two countries are identical .
the second is symbolic function .
to a certain extent , military uniforms are not only a reflection of a country 's spiritual outlook and national characteristics , but also a concentrated expression of a country 's military 's combat capability and military personnel 's accomplishment .
among the three major categories of military uniforms , namely , dresses , regular clothes , and training uniforms , there is nothing more capable of fully displaying national prestige and military prestige than straightforward and beautiful dresses .
the third is the protective function .
with the rapid development of new and high - tech weapons and equipment , improving the comprehensive protective performance of new - style training uniforms has enabled the uniforms to have a variety of functions , such as bulletproof , anti - detection , chemical , bacteriological , and radiation protection , as well as temperature , humidity , and air conditioning . this has become the most important issue in the development of military uniforms .
( Shi Wei )
party committee organs of a certain brigade dare to deal with thorny issues seriously
Xinhua news agency , Chengdu , july 3 ,
qu yumao and yang ruiyu reported : we were able to live in apartments thanks to the determination and courage of the party committee organs of the brigade to clean up houses .
today , more than a dozen cadres of a communications training brigade of the Chengdu military region relocated to apartments were all elated with joy . they were full of admiration and gratitude for the brigade 's party committee and the brigade 's work style of daring to deal with thorny problems rather than tough ones .
a few years ago , with the change of personnel , some of the family buildings of this brigade were occupied in violation of regulations , making it difficult for serving cadres to live in houses . officers and men had a rather strong opinion on this .
the brigade has also cleaned houses several times , all of which have remained unresolved due to various kinds of resistance , making this issue an old and difficult one .
as long as he dares to be serious and reasonable , there will be no problem that cannot be solved .
after the new party committee reached a consensus , the principal leaders personally came forward and began to thoroughly straighten out all the problems of illegal occupation of houses .
on the one hand , they moved with emotion and reason , hoping that relevant personnel would take the overall situation into consideration , and on the other hand , they explained clearly the relevant policies and regulations for military apartment houses , fund - raising houses , and economically applicable houses , thus demonstrating the party committee 's firm determination and principled stand .
with regard to some personnel who have housing elsewhere but are unwilling to withdraw from overoccupied housing , party committee organs promptly contacted their units and adopted corresponding measures to urge them to take the initiative to cooperate with the work of the troops .
after two months of meticulous work , all the residents in the barracks who violated regulations and overoccupied their houses moved out on schedule , and all the serving cadres of the brigade were given housing according to regulations .
the brigade 's party committee 's style of daring to confront a tough situation has also produced a chain effect . several cadres who were unwilling to actively cooperate in the organization 's assignment have now successively indicated their obedience to the organization 's decision .
