Jingjiang People &apos;s Armed Forces Department Establishes Platform to Improve the Quality of Specialized Military Cadres
on june 18 , at a training class for specialized military cadres in jingjiang city , Jiangsu province , lu yuqing , minister of armed forces of xilai town , gave a tutorial on " psychological warfare under informationization conditions , " which was unanimously praised by the participants .
this is a new change made by the city 's people 's armed forces department in light of the actual conditions of its posts and in its efforts to enhance the comprehensive quality of specialized military cadres .
at the beginning of this year , the party committee of the ministry of human resources and armed forces , while conducting investigations and studies at the grass - roots level , discovered that some specialized military cadres had long terms of office and held too many concurrent posts , and did not devote their main energies to the armed work .
to this end , they have adopted such methods as centralized training , acting on behalf of the congress , and relying on local party schools to train specialized military cadres on a regular basis , and have made efforts to solve the problems of limited knowledge and single professional quality among specialized military cadres .
in connection with the work of the center , it is necessary to boldly assign tasks and burdens to specialized military cadres , and enhance their ability to hold office through job training .
at the same time , they actively coordinated with local organizational departments and jointly formulated the " plan for the competitive recruitment of specialized military cadres , " explicitly stipulating that armed ministers must be promoted to the leading bodies of party committees at the same level and must no longer concurrently hold other posts .
a mechanism has been set up for the adjustment and exchange of specialized military cadres . for some older specialized military cadres who are not suited to the armed work at the grass - roots level , exchanges have been readjusted in a timely manner , and comrades with good overall quality and strong work ability have been promoted and used .
not long ago , Chen yisong , director of the armed forces department of the new century shipbuilding company , Ltd. , led a militia technical detachment to innovatively develop underwater ship welding technology to fill a domestic gap and was promoted to the armed forces department head of the company .
