the Ministry of Public Security awarded the Guangdong Border Guard Hospital the Second Class Merit of the Collective
Xinhua , Shenzhen , july 18 ,
Li Guoliang and Huang qi reported : over the years , while doing a good job in providing medical support to the troops , the Guangdong frontier defense corps hospital has spared no effort to help the masses in need and has nurtured the hearts of the people of all sides with love .
this morning , the ministry of public security held a grand ceremony in Shenzhen to celebrate the second - class collective commendation of the Guangdong frontier defense corps hospital and to report on the advanced deeds of supporting the government and cherishing the people .
in order to build social harmony , the Guangdong frontier defense corps hospital has set up three affordable hospitals in Shenzhen , namely , buji , longhua , and baoan , which are specially designed for migrant workers . migrant workers only need 1 yuan for registration , and the examination fee and operation fee can be reduced by 20 percent .
the hospital is specially equipped with a care service vehicle to transport peasant workers ' patients to hospital free of charge , and has also introduced the peasant workers ' health service card , which allows them to enjoy 12 basic medical examinations and guarantees for as little as 7 yuan per month .
this measure for the benefit of the people has benefited more than 12,000 peasant workers .
since 2003 , the hospital has also launched a large - scale voluntary consultation drive to light 1,000 lights and send ophthalmologists to Tibet , Jiangxi , Yunnan , Qinghai , and other places to see off light and healthy people . nearly 3,000 cataract surgeries have been performed free of charge , enabling patients to see the light again .
on august 1 st , the armed police force changed into style 07 clothes .
starting from august 1 , the armed police force will change into a series of 07 - style clothes .
today , this reporter saw from the ceremony and demonstration activities of the armed police force 's style 07 clothing that there are a total of 105 varieties of the new type 07 clothing , including dresses , regular clothes , training clothes , and logo clothing .
the color of the garments has been adjusted from the current olive green to dark olive green . the cuffs and side seams of the trousers all have decorative bands . the overall design has a strong sense of the times . in the setting of the size type , reference is made to the national clothing size standard .
the female officers and men 's big eaves were changed to rolled eaves , the police officers ' winter regular clothes were changed from the close - necked ones to the open - necked ones , the summer regular clothes were changed to a waist - girdle structure , and the spring and autumn regular clothes were changed to a hunting - style design .
the newly added nameplates , grade qualifications badges , national defense service badges and ribbons , as well as the redesigned cap badges , chest badges , necklaces , shoulder badges , and armbands , have enhanced the clothing identification function and enhanced the sense of beauty .
the style 07 uniform of the armed police will be changed in three years .
before 1 august 2007 , police officers , civilian cadres , and national flag escorts , military orchestras , and cultural troupes will be given dresses simultaneously with the whole army , and police officers , civilian cadres , and soldiers stationed in beijing will be given spring and autumn regular clothes , summer regular clothes , and logo clothing .
in may 2008 , soldiers and cadets of other units were given spring and autumn uniforms , summer uniforms , and logo clothing .
in october 2008 , police officers were given new winter clothes and overcoats .
in december 2009 , the soldiers were given new winter uniforms .
the training will be subject to gradual renewal with the seasons starting from 2008 .
a base of the Second Artillery Corps has begun operation in the Xiaosan , Yuan , Naoko Education Collaboration Area .
the phenomenon of small , scattered , remote , and directly administered units having difficult educational organization , few resources , and fighting their own battles will become history at a certain base of the second artillery corps .
this reporter recently learned that after half a year of experiments , the base has issued " procedures for implementing the ' outline for ideological and political education ' , " and a number of cooperative areas for ideological and political education covering all small , scattered , remote , and directly administered units of the base have officially been put into operation .
in order to promote the effective implementation of the " outline for ideological and political education , " the base organized forces at the beginning of the year to conduct in - depth investigations and studies on the current situation of ideological and political education in small , scattered , remote , and directly administered units , sorting out the key problems that affect and restrict the time , personnel , and results of education , and initially forming a new educational model of cooperative areas for small , scattered , remote , and directly administered units .
the specific practice in the cooperative areas is to break down the organizational boundaries of units , designate a brigade - and regiment - level unit to take the lead in the relatively concentrated areas of small , scattered , remote , and direct units , and carry out unified planning for thematic education , with units with different subordinate relationships attending lectures nearby on the same platform or using video systems for remote discussion .
we should adopt the method of combining rotational teaching with competitive appointment , uniformly deploy the educational force , uniformly use regional educational hardware , share and exchange information , data , and educational experiences of various units , and regularly organize regional typical tour reports and exchange and study experiences among officers and men .
full - time education focal points and part - time education information gathering officers have been established in each collaboration area .
on this basis , various cooperation areas have also established a system of asking for help with difficult problems , discussing major educational topics , and reporting and evaluating emergency ideological situations .
Zhang shengmin , director of the base 's political department , told reporters that the establishment of political education cooperation zones has not only reduced waste of educational resources , but also deepened educational results .
fearing losing points in front of officers and men of foreign units , some political teachers took the initiative to study new knowledge and explore new methods of education .
the officers and men who were educated also actively digested the contents of the education , fearing that they would make unfamiliar remarks in front of the officers and men of friendly and neighboring units during the discussion and analysis .
in this way , the enthusiasm of both educators and educatees is effectively aroused .
