a certain unit of the Jinan military region has opened its affairs to the public , so it is not hot in the hot spots .
Shimbun news
Wang weiqin and special correspondent li deying reported : on 25 july , at a service company of a certain unit of the Jinan military region , this reporter saw a public notice board with important items such as the bidding for military projects , financial expenses , the promotion of cadres , and the entry of noncommissioned officers into the party , which was hanging conspicuously in the window .
according to political commissar su chengsen , this is a concrete measure taken by the ministry to promote the open system of handling affairs .
at the beginning of this year , the party committee of this unit , in order to strengthen the building of a sound party style and a clean government , formulated such measures as " two - way supervision of organs at the grass - roots level " and " publicity of sensitive issues , " and demanded that all major issues concerning the immediate interests of officers and men and the building of the unit be decided after listening to the opinions of officers and men at the grass - roots level , and that the work standards , procedures , and results be made public throughout the process according to circumstances .
the unit has set up suggestion boxes and public notice boards , set up message boards on the local area network , and extensively collected opinions and suggestions from everyone .
at the beginning of the year , before the renovation and transformation of the soldiers ' dormitory building began , party committee organs extensively solicited the opinions of officers and men , and then issued tender information and implemented open bidding .
this has not only saved money , but also won the support of officers and men .
the practice of handling affairs in an open and fair manner has spurred the formation of a good atmosphere at the grassroots level .
in this unit , grass - roots companies persist in regularly publicizing and publicizing and consciously accepting the masses ' supervision over everything from the determination of major and hot - spot sensitive matters to the daily expenses of personal family visits and vacations and food accounts .
( international ) study on association between atrial fibrillation and two genetic variations
Xinhua news agency , london , july 2 , Icelandic scientists found through research that the risk of developing atrial fibrillation is much higher in people with two genetic mutations in their bodies than in the general population .
according to a report in the latest issue of the journal Nature , researchers from the Icelandic decoder Genetics Company obtained the above findings after screening the genes of thousands of people from Iceland , Sweden , the United States , and Hong Kong , China .
the two genes were found to be similar to a gene that played an important role in the early stages of heart development .
atrial fibrillation , or atrial fibrillation , is one of the most common clinical arrhythmias that can cause palpitations , shortness of breath , fatigue , and stroke .
in addition , according to a report in the " nature genetics " magazine published on the 1 st , the researchers from Asahi decoding genetics company also found two genes related to the incidence of prostate cancer on human chromosome 17 . they played a certain role in more than one - third of prostate cancer cases .
the study also found that one of the genes not only increases the risk of prostate cancer but also lowers the risk of type ii diabetes .
