Xinhua news agency , Maracaibo , Venezuela , july 3 ,
according to Venezuelan media reports on the 3 rd , the 37 - year - old us goalkeeper Keller said in an interview here that if he could not find a suitable club to play after the americas cup , he would choose to retire .
if i cannot get a contract of one to two seasons for a high - level league team four to six weeks after the conclusion of the americas cup , then retirement may be a good option for me .
with menshingrad Bach relegated to the second division , Keller also left the team , which he has played for more than two seasons .
although Keller has the heart to stop , he is obviously not worried about getting married , and he himself frankly said that up to eight teams are now interested in joining him .
however , this old goalkeeper , who has played in la Liga , the english premier league and the Bundesliga , said that his final choice will depend on his family . my child is nine years old . he has stayed with me in three different countries and attended three different schools . my choice now is to consider how it will be more beneficial to my family .
in the golden cup , which ended not long ago , keller played an outstanding role in helping the us team win the championship .
in this year 's americas cup , he was still entrusted with a heavy task by coach Bradley . however , he was unable to defeat four hands with one punch . the united states team , which played with the young guards in tajikistan , was not at all such a formidable opponent in south america as argentina and Paraguay . in two matches , he had seven holes through the gate he had guarded .
the next game against colombia is likely to be the final performance of the united states and Keller in this year 's americas cup .
