( international ) DPRK , ROK to hold sixth general - level talks
Xinhua news agency , Pyongyang , july 16 ,
military representatives of the democratic people 's republic of korea ( DPRK ) and the republic of korea ( ROK ) held routine contacts at Panmunjom on 16 july . the two sides agreed to hold the sixth general - level talks from 24 to 26 june .
according to a report by the Korean central news agency , DPRK military representative and senior colonel park Lim Soo of the Korean people 's army put forward a proposal for establishing a joint fishing zone between Yeonpyeong island and paekyong island in the western waters of the DPRK during that day 's contacts , and gave a detailed explanation of his reasons .
he said : to set up a joint fishing zone , it is necessary to implement the principles of maximizing the common prosperity of the nation and ensuring peaceful and stable fishing operations .
commenting on the issue of the maritime boundary between the two sides , park Lim - su said : in order to prevent military conflicts between the two sides in the western waters , the two sides should abandon the maritime boundary that they have adhered to so far , recognize and respect each other 's territorial rights , and take the relevant agreements between the DPRK and the ROK , the Korean armistice agreement , and internationally recognized laws as the basis for consultations .
he said : formulating military support measures in a timely manner to promote cooperation and exchanges between the DPRK and the ROK is the consistent stand of the DPRK military .
he said : at present , the ROK side should take military measures to ensure that DPRK civilian vessels can leave the port of Haeju directly and travel southwards and freely through the Cheju strait .
this is the second routine contact between the DPRK and ROK military talks held recently after 10 october .
the fifth general - level talks between the DPRK and the ROK were held from 8 to 11 may on the Korean side of Panmunjom .
( international ) Hyundai denies intention to acquire Volvo
Xinhua news agency , Seoul , july 18 , a spokesman for south korea 's Hyundai motor company said in Seoul on the 18th that the company has no intention of acquiring any brand owned by Volvo or Ford motor .
both the Sunday Times and the New York Times recently reported on Ford &apos;s possible sale of Volvo .
the Sunday Times even reported that Hyundai Motor Company of South Korea is a potential buyer of Volvo .
a spokesman for Hyundai motor company said : we are not interested in acquiring Volvo , jaguar , or land rover at all . at present , he is too busy implementing his own expansion plan to attend to him at all .
in 1999 , Ford paid 6.45 billion us dollars for the Volvo brand from sweden 's Volvo group .
Volvo , Land Rover and Jaguar are now part of Ford &apos;s Chief Automobile Group ( PAG ) .
Ford , which lost money in march this year , sold PAG 's Aston martin for $ 848 million , and last month it said it would consider selling land rovers and jaguars .
Cuba complains that boxing ropes are too short
Xinhua news agency , rio de Janeiro , july 21 st , by reporter weihua Chen and tong Leng
the Cuban delegation complained on the 21st that the short ropes in the boxing ring of the inter - american games would affect the boxers ' performance .
according to the rules of the international boxing federation , the rope length of the boxing ring in an international competition should be 6.1 meters . however , according to measurements by the coach of the boxing team of the Cuban delegation , pedro monteloc , the rope length of the boxing ring in this inter - american games is more than 1 meter shorter than the standard .
Roark said : " we have submitted an official protest because this incident does not affect a single country in Cuba , but involves everyone .
too short a rope can interfere with the boxers &apos; evasive movements .
he also joked that if he could not find a rope in rio that conforms to the olympic standards , he could look elsewhere .
if we had known , we would have brought it from Cuba .
delegations from Mexico and Colombia also expressed dissatisfaction with the length of the ring ropes on the same day .
although Colombian boxer Julio delbis won the first match , he said : " although i won the first match , the boxing ring was too narrow and i really felt uncomfortable . "
big White Rabbit Milk Sugar Restored for Export to Overseas Distributors Additional Order
Xinhua news agency report of july 24 from Shanghai ( by staff reporters Xu shousong and yu Lihong ) - reporters learned from the guanshengyuan ( group ) company , Ltd. that the big white rabbit milk candy , which once remained in Shanghai port , has recently resumed export , and many overseas distributors have also requested additional orders one after another .
Mr. Lin qingrong , a distributor of guansheng park in Singapore and a member of the funan company , recently telephoned the guansheng garden group , saying that since the results of sampling tests conducted by the Singapore agrifood and veterinary bureau showed that the rabbit milk candy was free of formaldehyde , it could be sold normally in the market , he requested an additional order .
Fengsheng , a Malaysian distributor of Guansheng park , said it asked Guansheng park to immediately ship a container of white rabbit milk candy from Shanghai to malaysia .
Kwan Sheng Yuen 's distributor , wu Fung trading company limited , also telephoned Kwan Sheng Yuen and said that the Hong kong food safety centre had taken milk sugar samples from the Hong kong supermarket and laboratory tests had confirmed that there was no formaldehyde in the samples .
Wu Fung trading co . , Ltd. has been informed by the china resources supermarket in Hong kong that it has decided to resume the sale of white rabbit milk candy in more than 100 stores in Hong kong .
it has been learned that 10 containers of white rabbit milk sugar , which were once stranded in Shanghai port , have been gradually resumed for export .
at present , seven containers of white rabbit milk candy are being shipped to countries such as Singapore , costa rica , malaysia , india , Nepal , and the united states .
( international ) suspect arrested for bomb threat in british supermarket
Xinhua news agency , london , july 26 , the british police announced on the 26th that the criminal suspect responsible for the bomb threat at the Antelope supermarket in britain in mid - july was arrested in Clithello , Lancaster county , on the 23rd .
police said Philip McHugh , 51 , unemployed , would be charged with blackmail and bomb scare .
on the afternoon of july 14 ( Saturday ) , police shut down 14 souvenir bazaar supermarkets across the uk because of bomb threats and did not resume business until the next day .
Saturday was the peak time for british people to go shopping in supermarkets , when the closure of 14 supermarkets cost the largest supermarket chain in britain millions of pounds in sales revenue .
the british police then launched a criminal investigation into the bomb threat and announced that there were no signs of terrorist activities in the incident , but there may be some economic motives behind it .
( sports ) Flowers Change Flowers for Beijing Olympic Games
Xinhua news agency report of july 28th from beijing ( by staff reporter cui junqiang ) - when next year 's olympic games are held , beijing is expected to become an ocean of flowers in hot and humid august .
through technical means such as changing the flowering period , researchers have found a good way to add color to the olympic games .
at the review meeting on the selection and application of new varieties of flowers for the summer olympics held in beijing on the 28th , the evaluation experts came to the conclusion that with the new technology of promoting controlled cultivation , different kinds or varieties of flowers in the natural flowering period can bloom at the same time in summer and achieve the best ornamental effect in august when the beijing olympics is held .
in summer in beijing , only a dozen kinds of flowers can usually be seen in full bloom , most of which are either dead or far from budding .
through their efforts , the researchers selected 206 varieties and more than 400 varieties of olympic flowers for the summer games .
at the 2007 olympic flower show held in beijing 's Haidian park , before and after the countdown to the first anniversary of the opening of the beijing olympic games , a group of flowers carefully cultivated by researchers who could not bloom naturally in august in the past will greet visitors with bright flowers .
( international ) turkey 's ruling party wins parliamentary election
Xinhua news agency report of july 30th from Ankara ( by staff reporter wang Jian ) - the final results of the 23rd parliamentary election announced by turkey 's supreme electoral council on july 30th showed that the ruling justice and development party won 341 of the 550 seats and once again won the right to form a cabinet with one party .
in the july 22 parliamentary elections , the main opposition party , the republican people 's party , won 112 seats .
the National Action Party won 71 seats in the elections .
in addition to the three political parties mentioned above , 26 non - party personages were elected to parliament .
Turkey 's new parliament will hold its first session on august 4 .
all members will take the oath of office and begin to perform their duties .
thereafter , the parliament will elect a new speaker by secret ballot .
the Turkish parliamentary election was originally scheduled to be held in november . however , in the presidential election at the end of april , the opposition party boycotted the only candidate , deputy prime minister and foreign minister Gul of the justice and development party , leading to the defeat of the presidential election , which brought the parliamentary election forward .
Central Discipline Inspection Commission , I &apos; m worried about the effectiveness of your = anti - corruption campaign
Tseng Koo - Chun sent a short message to Tseng Tseng - tsung at the 2007 - 07 - 02 14 : 41 Tseng Tseng - tseng
since 30 may , the central discipline inspection commission has given corrupt elements in all parts of the country a time limit of one month , that is , until 30 june , within which they must take the initiative to confess .
I , the grass - roots people , could not help but burst into laughter at this , the police caught the thief , told the thief a month in advance , and hurriedly came to confess on their own initiative , otherwise they would have arrested you , and where in the world is there such an anti - corruption force ?
isn &apos;t this tantamount to telling corrupt officials in advance to run away and quickly transfer the evidence of their crimes ? ? ?
what &apos;s the point ?
isn &apos;t that ... Hey , it &apos;s impossible to say .
anyway , even if it really works , what is the effect ?
can we curb and deter corrupt officials ?
we do not rule out that those who have the guts to do so will come forward to confess , but will they not run more ?
