the Key to Education in China : humanization
key Words : the Key to Chinese Education The Key to Humanizing Chinese Education
the purpose of education is to make it easier for the educated to live and enjoy in the existing social environment .
it is easy for all of us to understand this , but for all of us who live in a house like this , perhaps we can only simply understand it as having fun in a house like this . in fact , there are many categories of people who live in a house like this .
survival consists of increased physical strength and increased mental capacity
enhancement of physical strength -- through various kinds of physical activities , we should strengthen our physical strength , enhance coordination , continuously enhance our athletic ability , and meet the sufficient needs of our physical operation and the needs of dealing with the society .
2 ) the enhancement of brain power enables us to have a clearer understanding of the society in which we live , to know ourselves , to learn how to deal with others , and to acquire the ability to adapt to survival and experience enjoyment .
the above discussion on the purpose of education has little to do with this article . now let 's focus on the key point : humanization of education in china .
the essence of human nature is : we should fully understand the differences between individuals and not regard them as the same .
Club Original : several Common Stages of Learning from Buffett
Club originals : several common stages of learning from Buffett : I was walking
1 ) stage one : when we first get to know Buffett , if we feel that we have acquired the greatest treasure , we will immediately apply it to practice . however , at this time , we do not have a deep and thorough understanding of Buffett 's ideas , and we will often misuse many of them , misuse them , and misuse them indiscriminately , so sometimes the results will not be effective .
2 ) the second stage : after a period of study and practice , almost every intelligent person in Hong kong is considering several questions : for example , what should Buffett with chinese characteristics look like ?
should Buffett 's theory be used flexibly in china ?
can you do better than Buffett ?
therefore , at this stage , we mainly look for Buffett 's theory with chinese characteristics on the basis that we think we are and blindly think we are great .
after a period of practice , the results are often intermittent and unsustainable . if you are lucky , it is best to take some losses and turn back at an early date .
3 ) the third stage : after going back to Buffett , after several tortures , he finally realized that he was an ordinary person and not a genius .
we should be a little less demanding of ourselves , and it is completely enough to honestly learn from Buffett .
the simplest method is the most effective , but the simplest method often contains very deep principles , and only after we understand these principles can we better carry them through to the end .
the performance of this stage is that the short - term results are not great , the long - term results are many , and there is continuity .
4 ) the fourth stage : after Buffett has tasted the sustainable effect , this stage is basically intransigent to Buffett 's theory and totally dismissive of non-Buffett companies .
constantly studying and deepening his understanding of Buffett and using him in practice , the performance of this stage is that the results are getting better and better , and there is continuity , and he has entered a benign cycle .
the amount of time each person needs at each stage is not necessarily related to personal circumstances and luck .
