if an innocent person receives a death sentence out of thin air , will he be content to criticize the grammatical errors in the " award " ?
it was a winter day , and it was very cold in the youth center .
I do n't know who is on duty , and the stove has not lit a fire all day .
because legend has it that there was a strong earthquake , when we returned to our nest in the evening , we did not bother to start the fire again .
on the long pavement that can sleep 12 people , the four of us , wrapped in quilts , shivering in the dim light , played poker three times a night , and won meal tickets .
suddenly , a voice from far and near rolled in , and several of us only looked at each other for a moment and immediately realized the disaster was coming .
so he threw away his playing cards , flew down to the ground , passed through two narrow doors , and came out in droves .
as soon as we ran out of the dormitory , the poor thatched hut , made of stone , was instantly crushed to pieces .
we rushed into the courtyard as if we were standing on a rickety boat , tossing ourselves back and forth like restless men , unable to hold ourselves together .
in these few seconds , all the buildings around us , once they had a calm image of the past , successively shouted in a hoarse voice , danced a nearly mad break dance , and then turned into a plume of smoke to kill themselves .
naturally , the wires over her head were not willing to be lonely , and she ran away like a whip .
in front of us and behind us , the wreaking demons are releasing jubilant fireworks for their creations . the colorful earth lights can rival the beautiful dance effects of any large war movie . the roaring earth sounds and images support the drums of war , tormenting every fragile nerve .
at that time , there was only one thought : the end of mankind has come !
I can imagine the earth under my feet bursting open , the boiling lava issuing a fervent invitation like molten steel , and human beings falling free into the lava like ants , so stingy that they did not even have a trace of smoke and vanished in a flash .
my spine was numb as ice water , and the faces of a few of my companions in the gray were wavering like paper masks .
I wonder : will mankind thus bid farewell to this colorful world , and will tens of thousands of years of civilization disappear forever ?
but i am not yet over 20 years old , the flowers of youth have just bloomed , the joy of survival has just been felt , how i miss my beautiful life !
my parents , my relatives , where are you all , what are you doing now , are you still alive in the world ?
how much I miss you in the face of death &apos;s ferocious smile !
I don &apos;t know how long it was before I saw that the sound of the earth was fading away , the trembling of the earth was slowing down , and the fireworks were no longer flickering .
a huge ship jolted in the rough sea finally sailed slowly into a tranquil harbor .
a young and fragile heart was finally carefully put back into its original position after a near - madness ravaged it .
Earth , my home , you finally let us feel the warmth and warmth of home !
a feeling of happiness for the rest of his life slowly overflowed from under his feet like a warm current .
after standing firm , yu dou , who has just turned 17 , burst into tears in the face of the once harmonious and warm youth compound , which is now a ruins of ruins and ruins .
all the people were infected , tears streaming down their cheeks .
is the sky beginning to snow a mourning for the misfortunes of mankind ?
that year , the Haicheng earthquake killed a total of 1,000 people .
an expert said : fortunately , the forecast was made in time , and it happened before people went to bed . otherwise , a strong earthquake with a magnitude of 7.3 would have killed at least 100,000 people !
only a year later , the Tangshan earthquake broke out , killing more than 200,000 people .
