I saw a lot of cell phone projectors without a screen .
key Word : mobile Phone
the Korean company Iljin Display has launched a coin - sized laser projector module .
due to the extremely small size of the module , it can even be built into the cell phone , and a 7 - inch projection area can be seen on the wall .
( via ) the traditional projector consists of three different LCD panels , which are responsible for outputting three different video signals : Red , green , and blue . this small projector can convert three colors using only one LCD panel , thus reducing the volume and manufacturing cost of the projector .
according to an official statement , the LCD panel of the projector itself is only 0.24 inches long and can be easily integrated into the cell phone .
at present , more than half of the mobile phones on the market have built - in cameras , and it is estimated that phones with built - in projectors will soon appear in the market , but it is really hard to say whether the market will be optimistic .
